{"tid":1494734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要幫推］沙田柚馬友入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T00:40:32.000Z","uid":228656,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a481d40267039ce615a4029e19cdd7ae0a406069","tid":1494734,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqOPyeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqOPyeL.jpg&h=b6b94fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">823吐露的海萬人牽手 </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙田至馬鞍山人鏈，定咗路線係上圖藍色虛線。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">晚上7點集合</span></span><br />\n( 希望大家早15至20分鐘到)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8點正式開始</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 八點半亮手機燈</span></span>。<br />\n再次強調的是此活動並冇大枱<br />\n我只係借出平台幫手推廣，揾義工幫手係因為需要人 維持秩序同埋帶領人鏈。<br />\n但希望大家同心協力，一齊完成呢次( 吐露的海萬人牽手)活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集合點</span></span><br />\n1. 大圍火車站B出口<br />\n2. 沙田大會堂近城門河涼亭<br />\n3. 香港體育學院附近蛙艇訓練中心<br />\n4. 錦泰苑對出海濱長廊<br />\n<br />\n以上四個集合點以安排<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">義工</span>幫手<br />\n沙田友、馬友齊齊支持<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時見</span>"},{"pid":"48343bed5c2e282bfe99a3bb7bf2c07c7eda84ac","tid":1494734,"uid":76902,"like"